{
  "1811330": {
    "name": "不思议地牢",
    "steam_appid": 1811330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/115c11c8d7dd106ad7b5575be66413a8.avif?t=1768391833\" width=616 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在一个陌生小岛上醒来。这里受传说中的神秘黑魔王迷珀统治，他冻结了这里的时间，将整个小岛变成了一个令一切生物不死不老的牢笼。而他通过魔法实验制造出的各种诡异产物，则在岛上肆意游荡着。做好心理准备，你可能会在这里遇到食人梅子、爆炸南瓜或变异黄蜂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/70f37cb49fa174ef3d14d4575b9aa87a.poster.avif?t=1768391833\" width=700 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/70f37cb49fa174ef3d14d4575b9aa87a.webm?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/70f37cb49fa174ef3d14d4575b9aa87a.mp4?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/153ccb1760e03f89b55286a1c0cb3503.avif?t=1768391833\" width=616 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整座岛屿是一个巨大的迷宫，其中充满了奇异而危险的生物：奇臭蜘蛛、酸性史莱姆、火焰蛾子、咬人蜂巢——而这仅仅是冰山一角罢了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，你也并非手无寸铁。魔法剑、精弓、良盾是你坚定的伙伴，以及最重要的一样——勇气。你的英雄智勇双全、整装待发，时刻准备着投入战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/ef8a3e019ed4447157e1b7d355149e93.poster.avif?t=1768391833\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/ef8a3e019ed4447157e1b7d355149e93.webm?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/ef8a3e019ed4447157e1b7d355149e93.mp4?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/845597349789a33c13a6a818b99d2a28.avif?t=1768391833\" width=616 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，你还需要一颗机灵的头脑。岛上除了那些危险的怪物，还充斥着各种陷阱和障碍。无底洞、荆棘丛、尖刺陷阱……用你的聪明才智来渡过难关吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护好你的后背，推动远古巨石，去回味推箱子的快乐。解开配色谜题，拼拼图，逃脱那些像变异梅子的肚子一样黑的房间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/533bbc22a37d1dbedf83d509adfaaf36.poster.avif?t=1768391833\" width=698 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/533bbc22a37d1dbedf83d509adfaaf36.webm?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/533bbc22a37d1dbedf83d509adfaaf36.mp4?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/40896f2e1962dd49b67e40b6c5c603fb.avif?t=1768391833\" width=616 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >再勇猛的冒险家也不是铁打的。刚刚好，《不思议地牢》中设计了大量小游戏和副本活动。 来试试你运气吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/c041e8c836fe245c62cffcd6cce4213e.poster.avif?t=1768391833\" width=1600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/c041e8c836fe245c62cffcd6cce4213e.webm?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去掷贝壳，去开宝箱（但愿你能选对箱子，否则可能会被一把火烧掉眉毛哦），去钓鱼！也许你能钓上来一条金鱼，又或者钓上来一枚金币……也没准是一个炸弹，全看运气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/e786c55ac2b505093694f511513940f4.poster.avif?t=1768391833\" width=1600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/e786c55ac2b505093694f511513940f4.webm?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/e786c55ac2b505093694f511513940f4.mp4?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生活在这座岛上的不只有你的敌人，还有你的朋友。可攻略角色背景完善，个性鲜明，你可以通过赠送礼物来拉近大家的距离，与角色建立关系（开放关系也ok哦！）。毕竟，故事的最后，每个英雄身边都会有一位忠实的伙伴，对吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/d8a464be19c3f7c3607b7276ad4be7b7.poster.avif?t=1768391833\" width=1600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/d8a464be19c3f7c3607b7276ad4be7b7.webm?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811330/extras/d8a464be19c3f7c3607b7276ad4be7b7.mp4?t=1768391833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，岛上还有着各种各样“有故事的人”。魔石像原本是谁？他怎么会变成了如今的模样？渔夫为什么会有那么多的克隆体？他们到底想捞到什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切尽在《不思议地牢》，来游戏中揭开这座岛屿上的所有秘密吧！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 俄语, 日语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲",
